housands of jobs and generate more than $400 million a year in revenue for the Afghan government." SOURCES: Reuters, Bloomberghttps://www.reuters.com/article/us-turkmenistan-afghanistan-gas-pipeline/leaders-launch-start-of-afghan-section-of-tapi-gas-pipeline-idUSKCN1G70PUhttps://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-03-08/a-7-5-billion-pipeline-has-surprise-patrons-taliban-militants***]]></description>
