g tests in Tempe, San Francisco, Pittsburgh and Toronto."  SOURCES: ABC 15, Verge, Bloomberghttps://www.abc15.com/news/region-southeast-valley/tempe/tempe-police-investigating-self-driving-uber-car-involved-in-crash-overnighthttps://www.theverge.com/2018/3/19/17139518/uber-self-driving-car-fatal-crash-tempe-arizonahttps://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-03-19/uber-autonomous-car-involved-in-fatal-crash-in-arizona?utm_content=politics&utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&cmpid%3D=socialflow-twitter-politics&utm_source=twitter***]]></description>
